8 months new energy star certified luxury house built by probably the best builder in the city at the highest level of craftsmanship and material. Located at a very convenient location of Kanata in Urbandale Bradley Commons community by Terry Fox Drive and Hazeldean Road, close to all amenities such as Walmart, Food Basics, Lowe’s, Home Depot, Costco, Canadian Tire Centre, Water Baker Park and Kanata Recreation Complex. A few minutes drive to Tanger Outlets, Kanata Centrum and DND campus. Model of Discovery End comes with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms of around 2,300 sqft of living space including finished basement. Some highlights:
•	Hardwood on modern smoke grey color on the main floor, staircases and railings and all 2nd floor loft and hallway.
•	Contemporary elegant ceramic tiled ﬂoors in kitchen, laundry room, all bathrooms and entry.
•	High ceilings throughout: 9 ft ceiling on mail floor and an stunning 10 ft ceiling in the master bedroom of 2nd floor;
•	Very very large windows throughout;
•	Master bedroom comes with a French double door;
•	Extra-long kitchen island with quartz countertop;
•	Both main bath and ensuite washrooms vanity QUARTZ countertops come with double-sinks;
•	Upgraded kitchen hardwood cabinets with extra banks of drawers for pots and pans;
•	 36” higher than regular upper kitchen cabinetry allowing for extra kitchen storage; 
•	Luxury glass backsplash on the kitchen walls;
•	All kitchen appliances are the STAINLESS STEEL high end models; 
•	Smooth ceiling throughout;
•	Central air conditioner;
•	Basement laundry upgrade makes this house an extra 100 sqft larger than a regular Discovery end unit resulting in a very spacious 2nd floor;
•	Modern glass garage doors make the garage super bright. 
•	ENERGY STAR® Certiﬁed designates this Urbandale homes use 20% less energy than a house built to Code, with a corresponding decrease in energy costs.
•	LED lighting throughout home. 
•	For more details about this model, please check Urbandale’s website: https://urbandaleconstruction.com/models/discovery-end-unit/  

Virtual tour link for the builder’s model home: https://unbranded.youriguide.com/vW2SYDY74AXPD1
.

Available October 1st, 2020. Monthly rent $2,295 and tenants pay utilities (electricity, water, gas and hot water tank rental). Price applies to family only. Tenant MUST have excellent credit and stable income, No dogs please. Please email for showings.
44 Plank St.
Stittsville ON  K2V 0M4

Kanata townhouse, new, modern, Urbandale, DND

Beautiful detached home on quiet cul-de-sac features landscaping along front of house, covered front porch, well-lit double garage with inside access (4 parking spaces total), spacious backyard with huge deck and green area for gardening. This pristine house exudes pride of ownership, with replaced roof, furnace, windows, and doors (including garage) within the last 5-10 years. Main level boasts a hardwood floor with recently updated kitchen and stainless steel appliances. Upper level features 3 large bedrooms and a master ensuite tub. Finished basement includes a washer and dryer. The house uses central AC and gas heating. The neighbourhood is full of mature trees, and is a 3min walk from public transit (Route 93 to both LRT lines), schools (English/French and public/catholic), parks, and trails. Short trips anywhere you go, with nearby daycare, shopping, and recreation. Credit check required, no smoking.

///

Belle maison individuelle sur cul-de-sac tranquille avec aménagement paysager à l'avant de la maison, véranda couverte, garage double bien éclairé avec accès intérieur (4 places de stationnement au total), cour arrière spacieuse avec immense terrasse et espace vert pour le jardinage. Cette maison immaculée respire la fierté d'être propriétaire, avec le toit, la fournaise, les fenêtres et les portes (y compris le garage) remplacés au cours des 5 à 10 dernières années. Le niveau principal dispose d'un plancher de bois franc avec une cuisine récemment mise à jour et des appareils en acier inoxydable. Le niveau supérieur comprend 3 grandes chambres et une baignoire principale. Le sous-sol fini comprend une laveuse et une sécheuse. La maison utilise la climatisation centrale et le chauffage au gaz. Le quartier regorge d'arbres matures et se trouve à 3 minutes à pied des transports en commun (route 93 vers les deux lignes de TLR), des écoles (anglais / français et public / catholique), des parcs et des sentiers. De courts trajets où que vous soyez, avec des garderies, des magasins et des loisirs à proximité. Vérification de crédit requise, non fumeur.
